title: GOP bill would gut health law, halt Planned Parenthood money
text: [...] the bill faces potential opposition from moderate GOP senators concerned it goes too far and Republican presidential candidates saying it doesn't go far enough. The bill would eliminate the health law's requirements that most people who don't have employer-provided health coverage buy individual policies, and that most companies provide medical insurance. > ...
